# admin-modelservices.http —— ModelService CRUD（全局模型 catalog）。
#
# 路由：/admin/v1/modelservices*
# **v0.3 改动**：删 account_id（catalog 全平台一份）；删 group / spec_detail。
# 模型可见性走 admin-subscriptions.http（ account 订阅决定看不看见）。

### List
GET {{admin_url}}/admin/v1/modelservices
X-Admin-Token: {{admin_token}}

### Create
POST {{admin_url}}/admin/v1/modelservices
X-Admin-Token: {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_id": "openai/gpt-4o",
  "model": "gpt-4o"
}

### Get by model
GET {{admin_url}}/admin/v1/modelservices/{{model}}
X-Admin-Token: {{admin_token}}

### Update（model 是 URL 真相，body.model 被忽略；只改 service_id）
PUT {{admin_url}}/admin/v1/modelservices/{{model}}
X-Admin-Token: {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_id": "{{service_id}}-rotated"
}

### Delete (软删)
DELETE {{admin_url}}/admin/v1/modelservices/{{model}}
X-Admin-Token: {{admin_token}}
